partnerDetails.about: Electrosales Electrical Supplies (Pty) Ltd was established in 1973 and focuses on supplying Electrical Contractors, Builders and Maintenance departments with electrical goods and hardware. Electrosales Electrical Supplies (Pty) Ltd recognised the need to open a retail store that would cater to both industry as well as the general public.
